      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="2bb66-103"><xref:System.Windows.Markup.IValueSerializerContext>接口是一种特殊的形式的<xref:System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext>上下文，并且使用作为输入参数之一`Convert*String`  /  `CanConvert*String`方法的方式与相同的值序列化程序<xref:System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext>用于上下文`Convert*`  /  `CanConvert*`为<xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bb66-103">The <xref:System.Windows.Markup.IValueSerializerContext> interface is a specialized form of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext> context, and is used as one of the input parameters for `Convert*String` / `CanConvert*String` methods of a value serializer in the same way as <xref:System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext> is used for context of `Convert*` / `CanConvert*` for a <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2bb66-104">在 WPF 中实现的公共类型<xref:System.Windows.Markup.ValueSerializer>，因此使用<xref:System.Windows.Markup.IValueSerializerContext>上下文都位于<xref:System.Windows.Converters>和<xref:System.Windows.Media.Converters>命名空间。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bb66-104">Public types in WPF that implement a <xref:System.Windows.Markup.ValueSerializer> and thus use <xref:System.Windows.Markup.IValueSerializerContext> for context are found in the <xref:System.Windows.Converters> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Converters> namespaces.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2bb66-105">在以前版本的.NET Framework 中，此接口存在于 WindowsBase 的特定于 WPF 程序集。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bb66-105">In previous versions of the .NET Framework, this interface existed in the WPF-specific assembly WindowsBase.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bb66-106">在[!INCLUDE[net_v40_long](~/includes/net-v40-long-md.md)]，<xref:System.Windows.Markup.IValueSerializerContext>位于 System.Xaml 程序集中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bb66-106">In [!INCLUDE[net_v40_long](~/includes/net-v40-long-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Markup.IValueSerializerContext> is in the System.Xaml assembly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bb66-107">有关详细信息，请参阅[类型从 WPF 迁移到 System.Xaml](~/docs/framework/xaml-services/types-migrated-from-wpf-to-system-xaml.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bb66-107">For more information, see [Types Migrated from WPF to System.Xaml](~/docs/framework/xaml-services/types-migrated-from-wpf-to-system-xaml.md).</span></span>  
  
